items.name: ElyxLang
items.description: Elyx is a compact scripting language implemented in TypeScript and designed to run on Deno. It grew from a tutorial-based interpreter project and has been extended with many practical features including a usable REPL, classes, try/catch, switch/case, and packaging-ready CLI binaries.

items.name: Boltflasher
items.description: Bolt Flasher is an educational blockchain testing tool designed to simulate and demonstrate cryptocurrency transaction flows across multiple networks. It provides developers, students, and researchers with a sandbox environmentu to explore testnet BTC and USDT transactions, wallet generation, and blockchain data visualization.
